title: Honey Boo Boo has released a music video - watch it here if you dare - Theboltonnews.co.uk
text:
The young TV star, real name Alana Thompson, rose to fame on TLC's child pageant show Toddlers And Tiaras, followed by her own reality series Here Comes Honey Boo Boo. The show came off air a year ago, but it seems the 10-year-old has found another way to keep herself in the public consciousness - a pop song called Movin' Up.
 Theboltonnews.co.uk.
